Let us take you to the West Coast as part of our continuing culinary adventures
to highlight various regions of our vast country.
From the sprawling metropolitan areas of Southern California to the picturesque
coastline of Carmel and Monterey and to the rugged Pacific Northwest, the
Golden West is a land of scenic beauty and urban centers.
We hope you will enjoy your journey with us and have another opportunity to
Discover the U.S.A. with TWA.
